#. type: Title ###
#: 2020-02-14-newsletter-36.md:152
#, no-wrap
msgid "#Every Community Is Different"
msgstr "#每个社区都是不同的"

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-02-14-newsletter-36.md:156
msgid ""
"Alessandra Palange pointed out that **her [document](https://xrmuslims."
"wordpress.com/faqs-how-can-xr-engage-with-muslim-communities/) specifically "
"addresses Muslim communities in the UK**.  ‘We need to keep in mind that "
"**we are up against wealthy, powerful transnational corporations and that "
"the climate emergency knows no borders**. It’s important to nourish "
"identities that **connect us beyond a limited understanding of national "
"citizenship**,’ says Palange."
msgstr ""
"Alessandra Palange指出，**她的[文件](https://xrmuslims.wordpress.com/faqs-"
"how-x-engwith-muslim-communties/)特别针对英国的穆斯林社区。“我们需要记住，我"
